      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of article in May 11 Circuits section about easily applied hearing aid</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Because of an editing error, a report in the News Watch column of Circuits on Thursday about an easily applied hearing aid misstated the fitting method. While many other kinds of hearing aids require taking an impression of the ear and having the patient return weeks later, the new device does not.</p>
      </block>
